the singer-songwriter known for such hits as ``i walk the line,'' ``ring of fire'' and ``folsom prison blues,'' said thursday that his busy schedule the past two years has prevented him from doing ``all the things a 56-year-old man should do to keep track of how all the parts are working.''
cash flew to the hospital 100 miles east of los angeles after an engagement in las vegas, nev
cash was suffering from bronchitis and laryngitis which have lingered since a recent bout with the flu, the statement said
