the list of things the skater from sunnyvale likes includes soft drinks, rice cakes and mineral water, said leigh steinberg, his sports agent
that list also includes women, but the 24-year-old world champion in men's figure skating said at a news conference thursday he so far has no endorsements along that line. his training for the olympics left him little time for a social life, but boitano said he has plans to change that
it's been so long since i've been able to go out on a date or find a lady who can share with me the success i've had,'' said boitano, of sunnyvale, calif., who returned to the bay area monday night after winning the world championship in budapest
it shouldn't take the skater long
women send pictures of themselves along with marriage proposals,'' he said. ``some of them expect me to pick them up at the airport. it's hilarious.''
