i would say that i devote a good portion of my time
first of all, virtually all my time during the work week and a good portion of weekends is devoted to the business of the department and the attention that i've given to the matters of leading the drug policy board occupies a good portion of my time, probably somewhere between 30 and 50 percent of my time
