a. i'm talking to a lot of people of quality
hello?
q. is it your intention to stay on the job until the end of the administration?
a. well, again, i've told you before. i've never set either a limit or a deadline, but it is certainly my intent to carry on my duties as long as the president wants me to
i think that just about exhausts the questions
