while he termed the mayor's remarks unfortunate, hill added: ``i'm not going to even try to reach his level of negative campaigning.''
koch also said some people claim that criticism of jackson might be based on race, but he maintained that the black candidate's positions on the issues are just as open to comment as those of white candidates
he should be held accountable like any white candidate. not different. exactly the same,'' he said
