wheat for delivery in may settled thursday at $2.99\ a bushel, down from $3.05 the previous friday; may corn was unchanged at $2.09} a bushel; may oats fell to $1.61{ a bushel from $1.68}; and march soybeans advanced to $6.53{ a bushel from $6.48{
